<snippet><content><![CDATA[verify submission=${1}]]></content>    <description> /1 = verify the submission0 = do not verify the submission but assume that the link is submitted and will be visible there or is already (default) Even though this is the default behaviour, you should set it to “1” as used in most engines.2 = this submission step is not creating a link but is used for something else.Example: verify submission=1After a successful submission the URL is put to the verification list and checked in intervals if the link appears there.</description>    <tabTrigger>verify submission</tabTrigger></snippet>